This topic describes how to use *SignalFx Monitoring and Alerting for Pivotal Platform*.

##<a id='using'></a> Using SignalFx Monitoring and Alerting for Pivotal Platform

Use this integration to stream metrics about Pivotal Platform's health and performance into SignalFx. After installing the tile, get up and running quickly in SignalFx with the following features:

* At-a-glance visualization of key metrics in the [Infrastructure Navigator](http://docs.signalfx.com/en/latest/built-in-content/infra-nav.html#infra)
* [Built-in dashboards](http://docs.signalfx.com/en/latest/built-in-content/built-in-dashboards.html) for Pivotal Platform
* Documentation of the metrics collected by this integration in the [SignalFx Metrics Finder](http://docs.signalfx.com/en/latest/easy-charts/easy-charts.html#finding-metrics-and-events)
